"162","# Lindenius pygmaeus: iso. Richards: 1980

## Provisional Red List status: NE


## Red List Justification
Sole record is from 1956-07-23. This is the only record known, with the finder unable to re-find the specimen. It has not been found since in GB.

### Narrative
There are only 2 records of males – pre-1960. There have been no records since that time and there is some doubt over their identification (Richards, 1980). As such the species is not evaluated.



