"256","# Megachile ericetorum: iso. Perkins: 1925

## Provisional Red List status: NE


## Red List Justification
One record from 1844. Considered to be of very dubious presence in GB.

### Narrative
The 1844 record of this species was of a female and male specimen (Weybridge, Surrey). Other older records have never been authenticated, and it is a species prone to synanthropic colonisation. It is therefore not evaluated.



